  "detailed_description": "<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/496540/extras/068984ef0a777248ec077f3e0bd540d0.poster.avif?t=1618173993\" width=616 height=300 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/496540/extras/068984ef0a777248ec077f3e0bd540d0.webm?t=1618173993\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/496540/extras/068984ef0a777248ec077f3e0bd540d0.mp4?t=1618173993\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>Want to get your <strong>Highscore</strong> on the leaderboards? Chain kills to get combos while maintaining your charge bar so you can keep blasting away.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/496540/extras/0e31a5dea93d82685a2ec03a2b37794c.poster.avif?t=1618173993\" width=616 height=300 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/496540/extras/0e31a5dea93d82685a2ec03a2b37794c.webm?t=1618173993\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/496540/extras/0e31a5dea93d82685a2ec03a2b37794c.mp4?t=1618173993\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><strong>Upgrades</strong> let you customize the Prototype so it fits your playstyle.<br><br>Want to <strong>Speedrun</strong>? Find the best routes in every level so you can avoid conflict and turbo non-stop to the end.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/496540/extras/0ab2d41323f15a6d3e2c2f10b68578ee.poster.avif?t=1618173993\" width=616 height=300 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/496540/extras/0ab2d41323f15a6d3e2c2f10b68578ee.webm?t=1618173993\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/496540/extras/0ab2d41323f15a6d3e2c2f10b68578ee.mp4?t=1618173993\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>Zone of Lacryma too <strong>Hard</strong> for you? Press the brake button and slow everything down.",
